column5: Heading up to Canada in a few weeks and need a cheap & clean hotel between Eau Claire & Duluth for the night. Any suggestions? Thanks
badger motel - north of eau clair phish
Best Western in Spooner WI... home of the 24 hour hottub!
A nice super 8 was private motel for a few years in Black River Falls Wisconsin. Pool and hot tub.

Black Bear in Cameron. Mom and Pop motel. Nice and clean. Pull right up to your door, nice. Bar/ restaurant across the road with really cold beer and good food. Plenty of room for boat parking. Been there, works out great.

Tilldawg, if you contact WEMN 1410 radio station in Elgin you can get a Super 8 motel in Black River Falls for 20.00 dollars.First,call the motel for a reservation.Second,tell the motel you'll be using a WRMN certificate.Third,log on to the radio's web site and look under Hotels/Resorts You can order on line.Total cost is 22.00 dollars for the night.BTW,I'm using one for my trip back from Canada.
